		margin: 3px;
	}
	.lo_btn1{
		margin-left:40px;
		margin-top:20px;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
		height: 70px;
		width: 90%;
	}
	.lo_btn2{
		margin-left:40px;
		margin-top:40px;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
